</head>
<body id="page-top" class="index" >
	<div id="ip-container">
            <!-- initial header -->
            <header class="ip-header">
                <h1 class="ip-logo">
                    <svg class="ip-inner" width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 300 160" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMin meet" aria-labelledby="logo_title">
                        <title id="logo_title">Startup chronicles</title> 

                    </svg>
                    <div id='logo_my' ><%= image_tag "profile.png" %></div>
                </h1>
                <div class="ip-loader">
                    <svg class="ip-inner" width="60px" height="60px" viewBox="0 0 80 80">
                        <path class="ip-loader-circlebg" d="M40,10C57.351,10,71,23.649,71,40.5S57.351,71,40.5,71 S10,57.351,10,40.5S23.649,10,40.5,10z"/>
                        <path id="ip-loader-circle" class="ip-loader-circle" d="M40,10C57.351,10,71,23.649,71,40.5S57.351,71,40.5,71 S10,57.351,10,40.5S23.649,10,40.5,10z"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </header>
        </div>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-default" id="topbar" data-sr="wait 2.8s enter top ease-in 100px over 1s">
        <div class="container">
            <!-- Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display -->
            <div class="navbar-header page-scroll">
                <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
                    <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="row"  >
                <%= image_tag "profile.png", :height=>"71.5px",:weight=>"45px" ,:class=>"col-sm-3"%>
                 <a class="navbar-brand col-sm-3" href="#page-top">Home</a> 
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Collect the nav links, forms, and other content for toggling -->
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
                <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
                    <li class="hidden">
                        <a href="#page-top"></a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="page-scroll">
                        <a href="#chronicle">Chronicled</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="page-scroll">
                        <a href="#about" >About</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="page-scroll">
                        <a href="#contact" >Contact Us</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                    	<% if session[:user_name] %>
						<%= link_to("Manage",{:controller =>'admin'}, :class =>"action" )%>
						<%else %>
						<%=link_to("login",{:controller =>'admin'}, :class =>"action" )%>
						<% end %>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <!-- /.navbar-collapse -->
        </div>
        <!-- /.container-fluid -->
    </nav>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <%= image_tag "profile.png", :class=>"img-responsive",:'data-sr'=>"wait 3s enter top ease-in 100px over 1s"%>
                    <div class="intro-text">
                        <span class="name" data-sr="wait 2.8s enter bottom ease-in 100px over 1s">Startup Chroninles</span>
                        <hr class="star-light" data-sr="enter bottom move 50px">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
<section id="chronicle">
        <div class="container">

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-11 text-center">
                    <h2 data-sr="enter top ease-in 10px in 1.5s">Chronicled</h2>
                    <hr class="star-primary" data-sr="ease-in 20px">
                </div>
            </div>
            <%= yield %>
           
        </div>

    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="success" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                    <h2 data-sr="enter bottom move 100px over 1s">About</h2>
                    <hr class="star-light"data-sr="enter bottom move 100px over 0.5s">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div data-sr="enter top move 20px over 1.5s"class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-1">
                    <p>ournalism is a tool, which when used wisely and effectively, has the power to turn nothing into everything. With writers developing at every Facebook post and reporters going out of their way to grab and break news first, we believe that the essence of journalism is lost. It is about reaching out to an array of audience through just a few words, and Startup Chronicles help in doing so. The current generation does not believe in waiting for the opportunity to come their way, they take a leap of faith and risk their talents. </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5" data-sr="enter top move 20px over 1.5s">
                    <p> With Start-up Companies of all sorts emerging slowly, it is almost impossible to keep track of what’s new.</p>
                    <p>So do you have a Start-up company, YouTube Blog, Music Album, started a Food Joint, or launched Couture Boutique, authored a Book, or developed a Gaming App (so goes the endless list) and you wish it reached to a wider audience? Trouble having to collect revenue for advertising your genius, on paper? </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 text-center" data-sr="enter bottom move 20px over 1.5s" style="padding-top:20px">
                    <p><strong>Startup Chronicles</strong> will record your endeavour and write about events you’d wish to make popular. Free Unlimited advertisements on Social Sites will be an obvious part of the deal! (Who doesn’t follow social media after all?) We believe in active, updated and fresh reporting and what better than your Start-up, to archive? </p>
                    <p>We gladly welcome you to be <strong>Chronicled</strong> forever.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section id="contact">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                    <h2 data-sr="enter bottom over 1s scale up 20%">Contact Us</h2>
                    <hr class="star-primary" data-sr="enter top over 0.8s">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
               
                 <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2" >
                    <!-- To configure the contact form email address, go to mail/contact_me.php and update the email address in the PHP file on line 19. -->
                    <!-- The form should work on most web servers, but if the form is not working you may need to configure your web server differently. -->
                    <%= form_tag '/public/query' ,:name=>"sentMessage" ,:id=>"contactForm"  do  %>
                        <div class="row form-group" >
                            <div class="col-xs-12 ">
                               <%= label_tag(:name,'Name',:'data-sr'=>"enter right move 300px over 1.5s")%>
                               <%= text_field_tag :name,nil,:class=>"form-control" ,:'data-sr'=>"enter left move 300px over 1.5s",:placeholder=>"Name", :id=>"name"%>
                            
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row form-group" >
                            <div class=" col-xs-12">
                                <%= label_tag(:email,'email',:'data-sr'=>"enter right move 300px over 1.5s")%>
                                <%= text_field_tag :email,nil,:class=>"form-control" ,:'data-sr'=>"enter left move 300px over 1.5s",:placeholder=>"Email Address" ,:id=>"email" %>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row form-group" >
                            <div class="col-xs-12 ">
                                <%= label_tag(:subject,'Subject', :'data-sr'=>"enter right move 300px over 1.5s")%>
                                <%= text_field_tag :subject,nil, :class=>"form-control", :'data-sr'=>"enter left move 300px over 1.5s", :placeholder=>"Subject", :id=>"sub"%>
                               
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row form-group" >
                            <div class="col-xs-12 ">
                               <%= label_tag(:message,'Message',:'data-sr'=>"enter right move 300px over 1.5s")%>
                               <%= text_area_tag :message,nil,:rows=>"8",:class=>"form-control" ,:'data-sr'=>"enter left move 300px over 1.5s",:placeholder=>"Message",:id=>"message"%>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div id="success"></div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-xs-12" data-sr="enter left move 200px over 1.5s">
                              <%= submit_tag("send",:class=>"btn btn-success btn-lg") %>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                   <% end %>
                 </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="text-center">
        <div class="footer-above">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="footer-col col-md-4" data-sr="enter left move 100px over 1.5s">
                        <h3>Location</h3>
                        <p>Waiting to add<br> Phone: 09008230253</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="footer-col col-md-4" data-sr="enter top move 100px over 1.5s">
                        <h3>Around the Web</h3>
